{
  "type_id": 92825,
  "name": "Ymir",
  "description": "Following the escalating conflict of YC128, the Sebiestor Chief Acassa Midular called upon Core Complexion to create an elevated war platform capable of supporting the rapid response fleets she felt would be essential to Minmatar's success in the next war to come.\n\nCore Complexion took the Nidhoggur's classic design and elevated it with the latest advancements in fleet support technology. Superior command support technologies allow it to unlock greater speed and resilience for its accompanying fleet members. It is the ultimate expression of the Republic's military doctrine, supercharged by the technical brilliance that Core Complexion and the Sebiestor have become synonymous with.",
